@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_awlltw(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = 0.76
    v0 = wp.cos(wp.sin(0.03))
    tmp = wp.exp(wp.exp(wp.cos(v0 + 0.18)))
    tmp = v2
    tmp = (wp.exp((v1 + 0.11 / v2 + 0.62)) / (tmp + 0.10))
    data[tid] = v0
